nodes.text: This Republic droid served in the Republic Navy during the Clone Wars.
This droid was stationed on the Venator-class Star Destroyer of Admiral Dron on the main bridge during the mission to the agriworld Ukio.

The droid seems to be based on V-series droid supervisor, yet it is unknown if it belongs to the MerenData product line, which is described as "targeted for Imperial Military". It is still possible, though, that the droid is another MerenData product, similar in design.
